snippet.textDisplay:
🤣🤣🤣

You just made my day with this video! Thank you!

Poor Palpatine though he's so lonely without his friends and I feel bad for him... I relate to missing my friends and being so freaking BORED! However, I am still trying to keep the boredom at bay with: drawing, writing, and reading because those are my hobbies.

Never thought that villains would care either.

Voldemort has no nose so... wouldn't he technically be safe?🤔

Also I really want to see the other villains try to entertain themselves and their reactions to all that's going on especially The Joker's reaction to not fighting with Batman...that'd be so funny! He's be sooo mad!

I also want to see how Loki would react.

My favorite parts of the video were when Palps was dancing and singing, where he was roasting the fact that the Jedi fell from a cliff,the fact that he said "6 we'll stop there."-when he was pointing out that social media was fueling his frustration, and when he was lonely to the point of making puppets of his friends... honestly that was so cuuute! Because it meant that he does truly care for his friends and not only that, but they're a family...other than the fact that he has a biological granddaughter.

Anyway just wanted to share my thoughts and I love the message too.

Have a good day and stay safe!💖😄
